{"tid":493421,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"一萬蚊budget list 求評","createTime":"2017-12-08T13:33:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-14T16:09:30.000Z","uid":26380,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"5979a4d40744f981fcf79605a80f5cdc7ab6ee63","tid":493421,"uid":26380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T13:33:18.000Z","msg":"各位巴打求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一萬蚊BUDGET 想砌機, 主要用途都係想開高階畫質<br />\n玩上古ONLINE GAME個類遊戲, 砌左未來5年都唔換機了 <br />\n依家用緊個部電腦都十年前產物了...<br />\nLIST 如下: ( 都係參考下悠二巴打) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nCPU\tAMD RYZEN R5 1600<br />\nMotherboard\tGigabyte GA-AB350-Gaming 3<br />\nRAM\tADATA XPG Z1 (2 x 8GB) DDR4 3000 Mhz C16<br />\nDisplay Card\tGigabyte GeForce&reg; GTX 1070G AORUS 8GB GDDR5<br />\nHDD TOSHIBA DT01ACA300 3TB 7200RPM 3.5<br />\nSSD Samsung PM961 Polaris 256GB M.2 PCIe NVMe 3.0 x4<br />\nPSU Antec Neoeco II Series NEO-ECO2-550 550W<br />\nCase\tSharkoon AI7000 ATX<br />\n總計 港幣$ 10,079.00<br />\n都有問題想問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , DISPLAY CARD 個度我見悠二巴打係建議Gigabyte GeForce&reg; GTX 1070 WINDFORCE 8GB GDDR5,<br />\n咁其實同系列 G1 GAMING, AORUS分別大唔大呢?如果冇分別, 係咪唔需要加多幾舊水換GTX 1070G AORUS呢張卡?<br />\n多謝各位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"963cbac7a3ac35c844387e78026920fafd6740ed","tid":493421,"uid":98680,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T16:06:42.000Z","msg":"連登求評<br />\n<br />\n都係加多少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0c53f547c155ad4cf9eb5cd79df8a53b44f1be4","tid":493421,"uid":125477,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T03:46:54.000Z","msg":"既然砌到1萬就上到8700/ Ryzen 7 1700X GTX 1080喇"},{"pid":"da727340badbd57258a97b0343097ea0dc89cc72","tid":493421,"uid":26380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cite